2. the person driving the ship is the mechanic##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the person watching romance movies and the mechanic##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
