4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person drinking milk and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

